// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0077 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 630ca8f9-221d-5821-94b7-1587e2282d8a

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
